25:02.565 --> 25:03.405
lovely.

25:06.805 --> 25:09.005
-You forgot "sexy," but...
-Yeah, well...

25:10.405 --> 25:11.925
didn't want to be too obvious.

25:12.925 --> 25:15.285
-If you were 20 years younger, right?
-Exactly.

25:18.445 --> 25:21.565
Mind you, if I was 20 years younger,
I think I could do better.

25:21.645 --> 25:22.525
[Tony snickers]

25:23.325 --> 25:25.445
-Yeah, definitely.
-[Anne chuckles]

25:25.525 --> 25:26.885
[laughing]

25:27.805 --> 25:28.765
Ah.

25:35.125 --> 25:36.445
[Kath] All right, I'm off.

25:37.645 --> 25:38.485
Bye.

25:39.045 --> 25:41.285
-See you tomorrow.
-See ya.

25:52.565 --> 25:54.125
-See ya.
-[Sandy] Bye.

25:58.165 --> 26:00.245
[printer whirring]

26:29.725 --> 26:30.845
-[Sandy] Tony.
-Huh?

26:31.205 --> 26:32.565
Please be happy.

26:33.245 --> 26:34.205
What?

26:34.285 --> 26:35.965
[Sandy] You deserve to be happy.

26:36.045 --> 26:37.125
Please be happy.

26:38.485 --> 26:39.965
I love how much you love your wife,

26:40.565 --> 26:45.125
and I can't wait for someone
to love me as much as you love your wife.

26:45.725 --> 26:48.125
But... you can still be happy.

26:48.485 --> 26:49.445
Okay.

26:50.445 --> 26:51.645
[Sandy] You're so funny.

26:52.165 --> 26:53.725
You make me laugh all the time.

26:54.285 --> 26:55.965
Tony, you're breaking my heart.

26:56.045 --> 26:56.885
Okay.

26:58.485 --> 26:59.725
[breathes deeply]

27:01.845 --> 27:04.405
-How's the Brian story going?
-Yeah, I've got it here.

27:05.365 --> 27:06.885
-Do you want to read it?
-Yep.

27:09.725 --> 27:11.605
[sighs]

27:18.845 --> 27:19.965
[chuckles]

27:24.245 --> 27:25.085
Well,

27:25.245 --> 27:26.685
