27:27.845 --> 27:28.925
-Really?
-Yeah.

27:30.405 --> 27:31.525
Oh, my God. I could cry.

27:31.605 --> 27:34.445
Don't cry, and don't be too flattered.
Have you seen our front pages?

27:34.525 --> 27:35.885
[laughing] Yeah.

27:36.485 --> 27:37.365
But still....

27:38.085 --> 27:38.965
It's really good.

27:40.005 --> 27:41.485
-Really good.
-Thank you.

28:07.765 --> 28:08.765
[Lisa clears throat]

28:10.845 --> 28:11.845
[gasps]

28:13.445 --> 28:15.205
<i>No way!</i> [gasps]

28:15.605 --> 28:17.245
<i>Tony!</i> [laughs]

28:19.165 --> 28:20.925
<i>Oh, my God!</i>

28:23.085 --> 28:24.245
<i>Hello!</i>

28:24.325 --> 28:25.725
<i>Hello, you!</i>

28:26.365 --> 28:27.285
<i>Hello.</i>

28:28.885 --> 28:31.125
<i>Wow. This is your new home.</i>

28:31.205 --> 28:33.245
<i>-</i>[Tony, whispering] <i>Oh, God.</i>
<i>-My God, Tony.</i>

28:33.325 --> 28:34.445
[Tony] <i>Look at that face.</i>

28:34.525 --> 28:36.845
[Lisa, chuckling] <i>She is gorgeous.</i>

28:36.925 --> 28:38.925
["Fire and Rain" playing]

28:54.005 --> 28:55.045
-Hey.
-You all right?

28:57.005 --> 28:59.325
-I knew I'd find you at the office.
-[chuckles]

29:02.005 --> 29:02.885
Prostitute.

29:04.405 --> 29:06.085
[chuckling] Sex worker.

29:09.845 --> 29:10.685
