<i>♪ And you need a helping hand ♪</i>

29:21.205 --> 29:22.565
<i>♪ And nothing</i> ♪

29:23.405 --> 29:27.565
<i>♪ Whoa, nothing is going right ♪</i>

29:31.685 --> 29:35.125
<i>♪ Close your eyes and think of me ♪</i>

29:36.525 --> 29:40.125
