29:41.805 --> 29:43.805
<i>♪ To brighten up</i> ♪

29:44.765 --> 29:48.245
♪ <i>Even your darkest night ♪</i>

29:51.645 --> 29:56.085
<i>♪ You just call out my name ♪</i>

29:57.325 --> 30:01.165
